extendedInfo.description: Usage:* It's only available for Doremi Launcher* Download Doremi Launcher from Google Play* How to apply this theme1.After installation do not open it2.Go back to Doremi Launcher; open sidebar on the left; find Menu > Themes3In the theme store, click Apply buttton on the right side of "Summer Breeze" wallpaper4.Summer Breeze is loaded
